Subject: rPSA-2007-0038-1 spamassassin

rPath Security Advisory: 2007-0038-1
Published: 2007-02-23
Products: rPath Linux 1
Rating: Minor
Exposure Level Classification:
    Remote Deterministic Denial of Service
Updated Versions:
    spamassassin=/conary.rpath.com@rpl:devel//1/3.1.8-0.1-1

References:
    http://www.cve.mitre.org/cgi-bin/cvename.cgi?name=CVE-2007-0451
    https://issues.rpath.com/browse/RPL-1073

Description:
    Previous versions of the spamassassin package are vulnerable to a
    minor remote denial of service attack in which spamassassin may
    use an unreasonable amount of processor time to process certain
    email messages.
